name: Add Disconnect List, and improve database
body:
- The Disconnect List adds a standard list for blocking, used in the Firefox browser. Additionally, the "X-Ray" blocklist is included, shown as "Uncategorised" trackers.
- Legacy code is removed, improving the database layout

name: Improvements and Fixes
body:
- Reduce database size
- Auto-reload tracker details on reloading screen
- More granular consent flow to retrieve developer email
- Latest NetGuard version

name: Large update. Complete rewrite of monitoring and blocking functionality.
body:
- Higher network speed
- Reduced RAM consumption
- Fixes of various reported bugs
- Support for ad-blocking with hosts files
- Support for custom VPN
- Halved app size (now 5MB)

name: Fix various bugs
body: Address bugs with emails, scrolling, autostart, and Private DNS.

name: Fix bugs, exclude some necessary trackers from blocking.
Add GDPR requests and monitoring of system apps
body: The releases here are now without minification (minifyEnabled=false in AndroidStudio), therefore slightly larger apk.
